CGI::Widget::DBI::Browse - Database browsing widget

DESCRIPTION

CGI::Widget::DBI::Browse implements a database browsing UI, using
successive calls to a CGI::Widget::DBI::Search widget.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  CGI
  CGI::Widget::DBI::Search
  DBI
  Test::Unit  (for running unit tests)

